          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The mean neutron energy was determined by the Zr/Nb",
                "method."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Disks of natural germanium. Size of samples:",
                " 1)for diameter 10 mm, thickness 0.7mm;",
                " 2)for diameter 20 mm, thickness 2 mm.",
                "To reduce the influence of thermal neutrons the Ge",
                " samples were covered by In and Cd foils.",
                "Irradiation of samples was done at the 75 mm distance",
                " to T-Ti target at the angles 0, 120, 150, 45, 75 deg",
                " to axis of deutron beam, that corresponds to the mean",
                " neutron energies 13.32, 13.69, 14.35, 14.74 and",
                " 14.53 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
